        item: Size of item to be added to the bin.

def priority_v2(item: float, bins_remain_cap: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    capacities = np.copy(bins_remain_cap)
    priorities = np.zeros_like(capacities)
    valid_bins = capacities >= item
    if not np.any(valid_bins):
        return priorities
    
    waste = capacities[valid_bins] - item
    
    sigmoid_values = 1 / (1 + np.exp(-waste))
    
    priorities[valid_bins] = sigmoid_values
    
    return priorities
